  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_nhs_continuing_healthcare_referrals">NHS CONTINUING HEALTHCARE REFERRALS</xref>
 is the number of referrals for 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 in the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_reporting_period">REPORTING PERIOD</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A referral is the earliest notification to the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">CCG</xref>
), or 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 acting on behalf of the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>
, that full consideration for 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 is required, for example:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
For 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__fast_track_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Fast Track)</xref>
: the 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_fast_track_pathway_tool">Fast Track Pathway Tool</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
For 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare__standard_">NHS Continuing Healthcare (Standard)</xref>
: a positive 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_checklist">NHS Continuing Healthcare Checklist</xref>
 or other notification that full consideration is required.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>The following should not be counted as referrals:</p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
Negative 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_checklist">NHS Continuing Healthcare Checklist</xref>
, where a need for full assessment is not indicated        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/nhs_continuing_healthcare_local_appeal.asp"
                  scope="external"
                  format="html">NHS Continuing Healthcare Local Appeals</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/nhs_continuing_healthcare_local_resolution.asp"
                  scope="external"
                  format="html">NHS Continuing Healthcare Local Resolutions</xref>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Referrals for transitional cases aged under 18</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_previously_unassessed_period_of_care">Previously Unassessed Periods of Care</xref>
            <p>.</p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>


